title: Google\Cloud\Security\PrivateCA\V1beta1\Certificate
name: Certificate
description:
A [Certificate][google.cloud.security.privateca.v1beta1.Certificate] corresponds to a signed X.509 certificate issued by a [CertificateAuthority][google.cloud.security.privateca.v1beta1.CertificateAuthority].

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.security.privateca.v1beta1.Certificate

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data.name
params.description: Output only. The resource path for this [Certificate][google.cloud.security.privateca.v1beta1.Certificate] in the format projects/*/locations/*/certificateAuthorities/*/certificates/*.

params.name: data.pem_csr
params.description: Immutable. A pem-encoded X.509 certificate signing request (CSR).

params.name: data.config
params.description: Immutable. A description of the certificate and key that does not require X.509 or ASN.1.

params.name: data.lifetime
params.description: Required. Immutable. The desired lifetime of a certificate. Used to create the "not_before_time" and "not_after_time" fields inside an X.509 certificate. Note that the lifetime may be truncated if it would extend past the life of any certificate authority in the issuing chain.

params.description: Output only. Details regarding the revocation of this [Certificate][google.cloud.security.privateca.v1beta1.Certificate]. This [Certificate][google.cloud.security.privateca.v1beta1.Certificate] is considered revoked if and only if this field is present.

params.description: Output only. The pem-encoded, signed X.509 certificate.

params.name: data.certificate_description
params.description: Output only. A structured description of the issued X.509 certificate.

params.name: data.pem_certificate_chain
params.description: Output only. The chain that may be used to verify the X.509 certificate. Expected to be in issuer-to-root order according to RFC 5246.

params.name: data.create_time
params.description: Output only. The time at which this [Certificate][google.cloud.security.privateca.v1beta1.Certificate] was created.

params.name: data.update_time
params.description: Output only. The time at which this [Certificate][google.cloud.security.privateca.v1beta1.Certificate] was updated.

params.name: data.labels
params.description: Optional. Labels with user-defined metadata.
